headline: 3 HMO Stocks in Focus Despite Rising Medical Costs, Regulatory Pressures
summary: The Medical-HMO industry pursues growth through M&A and tech innovation, aided by easing interest rates, but faces headwinds from rising medical costs, regulatory shifts and a shortage of healthcare professionals. UNH, HUM and CNC are likely to navigate industry storms.
